Nona Zhou berada di Kota Lingling.

762
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:08,940
Dia pergi menjemputnya.

763
00:45:08,940 --> 00:45:10,090
Saat mereka kembali, aku akan aman.

764
00:45:10,090 --> 00:45:11,260
Apa?

765
00:45:11,370 --> 00:45:12,700
Fei telah datang?

766
00:45:12,700 --> 00:45:13,810
Ya.

767
00:45:13,810 --> 00:45:14,980
Xie Yun, kamu tahu apa?

768
00:45:14,980 --> 00:45:16,570
Dia adalah pewaris dari South Blade.

769
00:45:16,570 --> 00:45:17,700
Tuan Bai berkata

770
00:45:17,700 --> 00:45:19,050
saat kami di Huarong,

771
00:45:19,050 --> 00:45:20,740
Nona Zhou membantu kami

772
00:45:20,740 --> 00:45:22,090
dan menahan Demons.

773
00:45:22,090 --> 00:45:23,420
Jika tidak, kami tidak akan ...

774
00:45:26,500 --> 00:45:27,500
Xie Yun?

775
00:45:32,770 --> 00:45:33,810
Silahkan lewat sini.

776
00:45:34,500 --> 00:45:35,700
Penatua Bai telah datang.

777
00:45:35,700 --> 00:45:37,260
Dia bilang kamu menyelamatkannya

778
00:45:37,260 --> 00:45:39,180
