779
00:45:39,180 --> 00:45:40,330
Penatua Bai?

780
00:45:48,940 --> 00:45:51,940
Nona Zhou, terima kasih 
telah membantu kami terakhir kali.

781
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:53,290
Sama-sama, Tuan Bai.

782
00:45:53,740 --> 00:45:54,570
aku penasaran

783
00:45:54,570 --> 00:45:56,500
