792
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:15,610
Iya.

793
00:46:15,610 --> 00:46:17,180
Mengapa Anda menginginkannya?

794
00:46:17,980 --> 00:46:19,290
Sejujurnya, Nona Zhou,

795
00:46:19,980 --> 00:46:22,810
Pangeran Zichen mendengar 
tentang pola riak

796
00:46:22,810 --> 00:46:23,900
